		<turn type="student">Do you think Barcelona is safe for women? I am gonna travel with my best friend and she's worried about pickpockets.</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="Pi.ai">Barcelona is generally a safe city for women, but as with any major tourist destination, there is always a risk of pickpockets. üö´üí∞ Here are some tips to help your friend feel more secure:
