		<turn type="student">Which clothes should I wear to avoid drawing attention?</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="Pi.ai">To blend in with the locals and avoid drawing unwanted attention, consider dressing like a typical Barcelona resident. üëïüëñ Here are some suggestions:
