		Layers: The weather can be unpredictable, so bring layers to adjust to changing temperatures.
		Remember, the key is to be comfortable and practical while fitting in with the local style.</turn>
		<turn type="student">Why do you think El Raval isn't safe for women?</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="Pi.ai">While El Raval has a lot to offer, including a vibrant nightlife and cultural scene, it also has a reputation for being a bit unsafe, especially for women. Here are some reasons why:
