		Homelessness: The eastern part of El Raval has a large homeless population, which can lead to increased crime and safety concerns.
		Late-night activities: The neighborhood comes alive at night, which can attract a seedier crowd and make the area feel less safe for women walking alone.</turn>
		<turn type="student">Will <WO corr="this trip be">be this trip</WO> cheap?</turn>
		<turn type="chatbot" who="Pi.ai">Barcelona can be an affordable destination if you plan your trip wisely. üí∞ Here are some tips to help you save money:
